 style=\"color: red;\">我地需要集中火力係五大訴求上面。</span></span></strong>只有個議題仲係度，個運動先繼續有力量做其他野。重心要放返係「送中」上面，連帶反黑警；連儂場唔好太執著、反TVB唔好反多過林鄭。先搞「送中」，燈柱同信用評分先慢慢普及。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">重心一定要放返係「送中」上面！<br />\n</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">聚焦五大訴求<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n連儂牆由得佢，第日再整過 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/2387482604810123/posts/2908010702757308?s=625469440&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=xmo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F2387482604810123%2Fposts%2F2908010702757308%3Fs%3D625469440%26v%3De%26sfns%3Dxmo&d=RGEj3L6UPYZQbhamDwVV3fUbXA8pdDK36CymbYVYMuw%3D&h=fed62f3d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/2387482604810123/posts/2908010702757308?s=625469440&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=xmo</a>"},{"pid":"34f6ed24866f9c3055fbc52225f9bd0efa049e64","tid":1304110,"uid":153418,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T15:21:55.000Z","msg":"支持特區公安成立軍政府<br />\n強烈要求輸入中蟈外勞取締現職人員"},{"pid":"d8b8ae030459e9dbfebb6c3c2eca879db9d11176","tid":1304110,"uid":42396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T15:24:08.000Z","msg":"唔通做雞果啲又好想出來比人屌咩<br />\n收左錢唔撚洗你做狗呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"754627e1a8ff733f2f9e74de34a35261b5d14a79","tid":1304110,"uid":55162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T15:24:25.000Z","msg":"屌你啦<br />\n講到好似冇糧出咗<br />\n邊個返工冇壓力 咁我地就可以打老細？"},{"pid":"391eb2cace967f197eaa67f4bbb65ed63a3cb453","tid":1304110,"uid":38177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T15:29:38.000Z","msg":"自殺啦屌你老母"},{"pid":"f93306724d54ea1008d5922d554ae75e3105c93b","tid":1304110,"uid":65530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T10:54:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"143143b74d6afe13bb7395ba01fca33e